company_name: SONNENALM BÄUERLICHE VERMARKTUNG, REGESTRIERTE GENOSSENSCHAFT M.B.H.
information: The company SONNENALM BÄUERLICHE VERMARKTUNG, REGESTRIERTE GENOSSENSCHAFT M.B.H., which operates in the Fish industry. It also operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industries. It is based in Klein St. Paul, Austria.
